{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c8125b6529","title":"转发《代食品会议情况反映》的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e385bbb34f","index":0,"year":1960,"month":12,"day":12,"articleId":"c8125b6529"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji44","name":"毛泽东全集第44卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/44-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6f87d8e611","type":"title","text":"转发《代食品会议情况反映》的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c8125b6529"},{"id":"add2bc8ace","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c8125b6529"},{"id":"25e18976f1","type":"appellation","text":"尚昆同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c8125b6529"},{"id":"f85a36af12","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请你用电报发给各省、市、区党委阅读。虽然已过去一个月了，但是仍然有用。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c8125b6529"},{"id":"6ef6cff0c0","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东十二月十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c8125b6529"}],"page":{"id":"072b82b888","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c8125b6529","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji44":{"comments":[{"id":"637f60f3b2","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c8125b6529","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"},{"id":"f184535606","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c8125b6529","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指国务院财贸办公室副主任姚依林1960年11月12日整理的关于代食品会议情况的材料。其要点是：（一）各地代表一致认为谭震林副总理的报告明确了推广代食品的方针、政策，解决了很大问题。有的说，过去对粮食、蔬莱只重视数量，没有强调质量，只考虑如何用代食品填饱肚子，现在才懂得还要注意营养。今后要根据每种作物的不同养分来安排生产，为此要求科研部门提供各种作物所含养分的资料。（二）对于大搞代食品，各地劲头很大，一些干部已打电话回去，要求立即行动起来。（三）关于如何开展推广工作问题，各地都进行了讨论，打算建立机构，安排劳力，做好生产计划，进行技术培训。（四）大家一致认为，开展这一运动，必须做好思想工作，改变群众对菌类的看法，同时要解决一些实际问题。1960年12月14日，中共中央向各省、市、区党委转发了这个材料。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4aa1b3a0f7","type":"title","text":"转发《代食品会议情况反映》的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c8125b6529"},{"id":"637f60f3b2","type":"paragraph","text":"尚昆同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c8125b6529"},{"id":"9481d32697","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c8125b6529"},{"id":"b624d55715","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c8125b6529"},{"id":"f184535606","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请你用电报发给客省、市、区党委阅读。虽然已过去一个月了，但是仍然有用。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c8125b6529"}],"page":{"id":"c4066fa9ae","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c8125b6529","start":104,"end":104}}}},"__N_SSG":true}